data.description: Welcome to this beautifully remodeled 4-bedroom, 2-bath home, nestled in Deming, NM. This 1997 gem has been meticulously updated, ensuring modern comfort & style throughout. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a dedicated living room & dining room, offering the perfect spaces for formal gatherings & cozy family dinners. The spacious family room provides a comfortable & inviting atmosphere for relaxation & entertainment. The heart of this home is the kitchen, which has undergone a stunning transformation. New cabinets, sleek appliances, and gorgeous countertops makes it a chef's delight & a focal point for culinary creativity. Retreat to the master suite, a true sanctuary within the home. Featuring double sinks, perfect for busy mornings, a jet tub for unwinding after a long day, & a separate shower for a refreshing start to your day. Step outside to the back covered patio adorned with exquisite Talavera sconces & easy to care yard. Includes laundry room, 2 car garage, new windows.
